I originally made it a bnha oc but I’m still thinking about it…like, if i actually want it to be a bnha oc…

I only made like- 6 drawings of him only, so that’s why he looks a little different in those two drawings. I’m getting used at drawing him.

I’m still figuring out his personality. All I can say is, dont think he’s the typical shy anime boy lol.
